column2: Migrated from EPA STORET Legacy Database- originally reported by Wisconsin DNR
Same glasses- same method- name could be changed to mirror lake--beautiful!
Yesterdays winds whipped up the lake - cloudy.
I won't be sending any more reports this year because of the dam break at Mt. Morris.
Beautiful- could not be nicer- fall color starting.
Warmer. Cloudy. dark- overcast. still not a ripple.
Could change name to mirror. not a ripple-mirror like-beautiful-clear!
Again not a ripple-cloudy + mirror like.
Clear-sunny + still again not a ripple!
Checked line and disk - both okay.  Sky and water clear.
Beautiful day- could not be nicer.  Sky and water clear.
Beautiful sky and water.  Wonderful Wisconsin.
Partly cloudy.  Slightly windy and choppy.
Dark clouds.  Just got in as it started to rain.
Secchi disc clean.  Line ok.  Lake very still.  Slight ripple.  No clouds.
Sunny + bright.  Some clouds. little wind.  Slight wave action.
Slight ripple. some cloud action. sunny. best day of the week.
Overcast. slight ripple. cool sweatshirt temperature.
Nice sunny. scattered clouds. no wind. calm to slight ripple.
Much wave action. bright with clouds.
Some wind + wave action.  Clear sky.  Bright sun.
Still very slight wave action.  Sunny + bright. scattered clouds.
Measured secchi disc line- okay and the paint is good.
Sunny- partly cloudy- and waves and ripples on the water.
Just beat storm in- heavy wind and rain.
Slight wave action and partly cloudy.
Sky is clear- lake is smooth and very murky.
Some clouds- slight ripple- and lake is still very murky.
Clear sky- slight wine- wave action- and still murky.
Water still murky and partly cloudy.
Lake ugly and sky and temperature pleasant.
Nice day- some clouds- and the lake is smooth.
Beautiful blue sky and murky water.
Clear sky- slight ripple and wind.
Cloudy- seems like an early November day.
Beautiful sky and lake looking better.
Windy and cold- partly cloudy- and some wind.
Beautiful.  Some clouds.  Slight wave action.
Beautiful sky.  Clear.  Lake quiet.  No wind.
Dark clouds.  Ready for rain.  Lake slight ripple.
Slight ripple - nice with some clouds.
Some clouds.  Nice day.  Late summer.
Beautiful day - lake - sky - weather sunny- clear day. No wind.
Storm pending.  Thunder.  Cloudy in west.  East sky cloudy.  Slight ripple.
Overcast.  Still very still and very quiet (nice).
Overcast - with sun.  Very slight ripple.
Overcast with the look of storm clouds.
Hot- humid.  Lake low.  Beautiful.  Weedy due to cutters and skiiers.
Partly cloudy.  Rather still on lake with slight ripple.
Partly cloudy.  Some wind with waves.
Still and quiet.  Some wave action.
Some clouds from west - lake had some wave action.
equipment checked- good condition- lake very still- sunny- few clouds
beautiful- sunny- small clouds- slight ripple and wind
lake still overcast dark clouds- thunder shows hope for needed rain
clear sky- very slight ripple- beautiful after past stormy days
sunny with some clouds- slight wave action- no wind
lake very still sky clear- no wind
cloudy- rain probable- seems very nice on lake
Humid- overcast sky.  Some wave action.
Overcast with very little wave action.
Slight wind action with some wave action - blue sky.
Bright sunny day  - with scattered clouds - slow rolling wave action
Scattered clouds- weather and water beautiful.
Bright silver overcast sky.  No wind- no wave action.
Some clouds- slight wave action.  Another beautiful day.
After heavy rain.  Some wave action.  Cloudy- overcast.
Clear blue sky.  Beautiful with very slight wave action.
Some clouds. Water smooth.  No wind or waves.
Overcast sky.  Medium wave action.  Cool.
No wave action - clear- sunny sky - no wind.
Very still - clear- sunny sky - no wind.
Windy and rough with white caps - partly cloudy.
Calm- no wind or wave action - overcast sky.
Bright and sunny.  Water still cold-perch and bluegills biting.

column1: Harvesting has not begun- and plants are growing-  some visual obstruction due to plants.
abundant geese;  loons back in residence.  Eagles active.

column2: High winds and large chop on water High winds and large chop on water
overcast conditions with slight chop to water surface.
Choppy and murky Choppy and murky
slight chop on water slight chop on water
Lake very high from heavy rains Thursday.  Strong winds- many whitecaps.

column1: Lots of sediment from runoff due to rain.

column2: Beautiful day but much sediment in lake from runoff Beautiful day but much sediment in lake from runoff Beautiful day but much sediment in lake from runoff
Some minor sediment in water.  Calm day.  Bass are spawning in shallows.  Walleye are spawning at new rock grouping put in last winter.

column1: More eagles this spring.  My neighbor saw musky take down a mallard duck.

column2: High wind from north west causing high waves
Bright sunny day- with no wind.
Big storm coming- calm water but very overcast.  algae bloom in shallows. on south side of lake.  Pan fish biting.
Some algae in the water- minor bloom on south east shore line.
Rained during the night- no wind.  Large algae build up by shore.
Lake active with boaters for weekend.  Observed Eagle taking fish from lake.  Bass spawning near shoreline.
